{"tid":1178144,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"“熊貓杯”組委會官方聲明：收回韓國隊所獲獎杯","createTime":"2019-05-30T08:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T08:32:30.000Z","uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a98b4089a85da8d33f9ec203a3d9c4ff2c00f2e9","tid":1178144,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:19:51.000Z","msg":"虎撲5月30日訊據成都足協微博消息，經&ldquo;熊貓杯&rdquo;組委會研究決定，收回韓國隊本屆賽事所獲獎杯，並聲明不歡迎任何違背體育道德、體育精神的球隊及球員參賽。韓國隊也在今天上午再次向組委會鄭重道歉。<br />\n以下為成都足協發布的消息原文：5月29日晚，在2019&ldquo;熊貓杯&rdquo;國際青年足球錦標賽頒獎儀式結束後，韓國隊在場地內慶祝奪冠時，個別隊員在&ldquo;熊貓杯&rdquo;獎杯前做出不雅動作，相關照片被發布至網絡媒體，引發廣泛關注。 5月30日凌晨，韓國隊全隊在現場媒體見證下，向&ldquo;熊貓杯&rdquo;組委會及社會公眾公開道歉。同時，韓國足協也向賽事組織單位成都足協發來致歉函。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aN3v1tU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaN3v1tU.png&h=3c02b5bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v7QeJHh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv7QeJHh.png&h=29050e23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cffed862de3974981ef094ebfe4cd4145cc49b5","tid":1178144,"uid":45788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:20:37.000Z","msg":"韓狗vs支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03cd577e141cf613537319da93609d6a0572581","tid":1178144,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cffed862de3974981ef094ebfe4cd4145cc49b5","tid":1178144,"uid":45788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:20:37.000Z","msg":"韓狗vs支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"跆拳足球 vs 少林足球"},{"pid":"aac90b6c5243cd9666b09e60608db0d0cd2fe5ac","tid":1178144,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm